      "description": "Looking for a reliable way to get from A to B without breaking the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone seeking a practical and affordable ride. It's a great opportunity to own a dependable car that still has plenty of life left in it!",
