    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by. I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and let me tell you, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-cared for, so it\u2019s totally ready to hit the road with a new owner today. It runs super smoothly and still looks great parked in the driveway. If you're looking for a reliable, comfy ride that won't let you down, this is the one for you! Feel free to shoot me a message\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
